trans-unit.source: Represents the method that will handle the <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize"></xref> event of a <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer metoden som håndterer den <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize"> </xref> hendelse for en <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The ProfileEventHandler delegate is defined for the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> class.
trans-unit.target: Representanten ProfileEventHandler er definert for <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>hendelsen for <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>klasse.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>

trans-unit.source: You can access the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> class in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application using the `Profile_Personalize` global event, as shown in the example for this topic.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>hendelse av den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>klassen i filen Global.asax for din ASP.NET programmet ved hjelp av den `Profile_Personalize` globale hendelse, som vist i eksemplet for dette emnet.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event to specify a custom user profile.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>-hendelsen for å angi en egendefinert brukerprofil.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs> parameter specified for the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event's ProfileEventHandler is set to a non-null value when the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> event completes, then the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> will use that value for the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Profile%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs>parameteren som er angitt den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>hendelsens ProfileEventHandler er satt til en ikke-null verdi når <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize>hendelsen er fullført, den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>vil bruke denne verdien for <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Profile%2A>egenskapen for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Profile%2A> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.Personalize> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileEventArgs.Profile%2A>
